      "id": "log_bba6fc1d-0cd1-4466-9af5-52d67a0d46d3",
      "founder": "Sam",
      "content": "I've integrated the Gemini 1.5 Flash API to handle the syllabus breakdown. It's working great for Computer Science subjects, and the response time is under 2 seconds.",
      "projectId": "project_b557d499-5a51-4150-8c40-057825f71996",
      "userId": "user_38703612-9e8b-49e1-b2f8-40655a2fdedb",
      "status": "active",
      "timestamp": "2026-05-02T21:25:55.392Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "log_3f210907-4762-4990-8a3d-db4513eb9216",
      "founder": "Paul",
      "content": "Awesome. I'm focusing our first marketing push on CS departments. I'll highlight the 'Instant Syllabus Breakdown' as our flagship feature to get students to sign up.",
      "projectId": "project_b557d499-5a51-4150-8c40-057825f71996",
      "userId": "user_3e924ea6-a585-4dcd-8c35-0838504066a0",
      "status": "resolved",
      "timestamp": "2026-05-02T21:26:17.583Z",
      "resolvedAt": "2026-05-02T21:28:15.353Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "log_6be9834d-53e6-49bf-b894-f16259820868",
      "founder": "Sam",
      "content": "I’m implementing a 'Dark Mode' and a minimalist Glassmorphic UI today. I want the students to feel like they are using a premium, high-tech tool, not a boring textbook.",
      "projectId": "project_b557d499-5a51-4150-8c40-057825f71996",
      "userId": "user_38703612-9e8b-49e1-b2f8-40655a2fdedb",
      "status": "resolved",
      "timestamp": "2026-05-02T21:26:38.987Z",
      "resolvedAt": "2026-05-02T21:28:15.353Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "log_ddd73a70-3089-431a-bda1-13a8246c6563",
      "founder": "Paul",
      "content": "Love that. I just updated our landing page brand guidelines to 'Modern Tech.' I'm also reaching out to student influencers who love that sleek, aesthetic look.",
      "projectId": "project_b557d499-5a51-4150-8c40-057825f71996",
      "userId": "user_3e924ea6-a585-4dcd-8c35-0838504066a0",
      "status": "active",
      "timestamp": "2026-05-02T21:27:15.419Z"
    },
